{"tid":615426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱克伯格被偷拍執狗屎 傳召攝影師問話","createTime":"2018-04-03T11:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T14:32:17.000Z","uid":76115,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"75f066892c5257701d6bdf33876bb35e9971f893","tid":615426,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:02:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180403/58027606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180403%2F58027606&d=mwDQPt1y6DjBgKsiltFnrpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=df7b8c3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180403%2F58027606&h=47bce788\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180403/58027606</a><br />\n<br />\n社交網站facebook近期牽涉洩漏用戶私隱的醜聞，英國攝影師斯卡恩（Nick Stern）炮轟「教主」朱克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）虛偽，對自己的私隱非常緊張。2011年他拍下朱克伯格清理愛犬便便的相片後，facebook竟派保安「傳召」他到facebook總部「問話」。<br />\n<br />\n「真諷刺，朱克伯格會用那麼誇長的手段保護自己的私隱－－但數以千萬計用戶私隱卻不在他的優先處理事項上。」攝影師斯卡恩（Nick Stern）說，他憶述在2011年4月，當年33歲的朱克伯格已是公眾人物，當天他見朱克伯格在街頭蹓狗按下快門，沒想到會有保安找上。<br />\n<br />\n斯卡恩憶述，當時保安上前跟他說了幾句，要求他到facebook總部，斯卡恩於是在保安「護送」下前往facebook總部，之後獲安排與兩名facebook高層會面，當時對方跟他說，他已侵犯了朱克伯格的私隱，指他無權追訪朱克伯格，又要求他別再偷拍。斯卡恩坦言，雖然對方沒有出言威嚇，但他當時實在被嚇倒。"},{"pid":"a87ff3e6678bf1fe173225473d4677151b0a7e84","tid":615426,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:08:07.000Z","msg":"成班賤民users有無畀狗屌過朱克伯格都知 朱克伯格自己就帶隻狗出街柯屎都唔畀得你地知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過班用戶都係自己傻閪 自作自受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nZuck: Yeah so if you ever need info about anyone at Harvard<br />\nZuck: Just ask.<br />\nZuck: I have over 4,000 emails, pictures, addresses, SNS<br />\n[Redacted Friend's Name]: What? How'd you manage that one?<br />\nZuck: People just submitted it.<br />\nZuck: I don't know why.<br />\nZuck: They &quot;trust me&quot;<br />\nZuck: Dumb fucks <br />\n(2004)"},{"pid":"de6cc5e19669850ee419d09fc98b92851b22dff5","tid":615426,"uid":55597,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"唔用 facebook, whatsapp, Instagram<br />\n<br />\n用 linux"},{"pid":"39803d48e9127a0eff66cb5df5b183d336c76e52","tid":615426,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光明正大，怕咩人查？</span>"},{"pid":"6b387a091b5951e8fa9198467a3b18c0bc8c1768","tid":615426,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39803d48e9127a0eff66cb5df5b183d336c76e52","tid":615426,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光明正大，怕咩人查？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:23:36.000Z","msg":"nothing to hide<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f94d878f47fa227d04b5fe01fa97824ff712b5","tid":615426,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de6cc5e19669850ee419d09fc98b92851b22dff5","tid":615426,"uid":55597,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"唔用 facebook, whatsapp, Instagram<br />\n<br />\n用 linux"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:25:08.000Z","msg":"Facebook/whatsapp/instagram: we are linux users too<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7278daa70ac9e3f4631a26e860637cf4169ed931","tid":615426,"uid":119450,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:27:20.000Z","msg":"美國有personality right<br />\n唔告你係人情 告你係道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /